					<p>Keep this Book of the Law always on your lips; meditate on it day and night, so that you may be careful to do everything written in it. Then you will be prosperous and successful.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container copyright text-center mt-4">
			<p>© <span>Copyright</span> <strong class="px-1 sitename">Minute Verse</strong> <span> @DateTime.Now.Year All Rights Reserved</span></p>
